Product Overview
Available in VOD, Live and UX versions, Brightcove Once is a cloud-based ad insertion and stream stitching solution. Brightcove Once VOD seamlessly integrates with existing systems for ingesting content once and delivering it everywhere via a single URL. Brightcove Once LIVE offers all the benefits of Brightcove Once VOD in a live streaming environment and ingests one high-quality HLS or RTMP live stream, enabling publishers to deliver that content to any Internet-connected device via a single URL.Brightcove Once UX provides all the advantages of Brightcove Once VOD, plus new client-side capabilities, including the ability to incorporate interactive ads, insert ad overlays in video streams, hide player controls to prevent fast-forwarding through ads and much more.




Features


                                            100% availability
                                        

                                            100% server side solution — no SDKs, plug-ins or HTML5
                                        

                                            Additional monetization opportunities through expanded ad units and pay-per-click models
                                        

                                            CDN agnostic, allowing you to take advantage of optimum CDNs based on geography and pricing
                                        

                                            Eliminates the effectiveness of ad blockers
                                        

                                            Integrates with any ad server — 1st party or 3rd party
                                        

                                            Integrates with existing apps
                                        

                                            Live and on-demand
                                        

                                            Personalized user experience — different ads per users for both VOD and Live
                                        

                                            Real-time, dynamic ad insertion allows for monetization – including breaking news
                                        

                                            Single URL plays out on any IP-enabled device
                                        

                                            Single transcode 1:1 ratio
                                        

                                            Supports multi-screen closed captions for LIVE or VOD content in compliance with FCC regulations
                                        


Purpose


                                    Brightcove Once is part of a suite of products and services that reduce the complexity and increase the profitability of publishing, distributing, measuring and monetizing multi-screen video.
                                







Pricing


                                One Time Fee (Project, Sponsorship or Outright Purchase)
                            




