Product Overview
Brightcove Zencoder is a reliable cloud-based service featuring fast transcoding, input file compatibility and output support for all connected devices.




Features


                                            99.9% encoding success rate
                                        

                                            AES encryption
                                        

                                            Backed by an uptime SLA and live support with real encoding engineers
                                        

                                            Complete adaptive bitrate solution for Apple HTTP Live Streaming
                                        

                                            Delivers best quality with device presets
                                        

                                            Enables publishing to any connected device
                                        

                                            File transcoding and Live transcoding 
                                        

                                            Industry-leading success and reliability
                                        

                                            Optimized HLS packaging with up to 12% smaller files
                                        

                                            RESTful API is documented with easy-to-use guides and detailed descriptions, as well as thoroughly tested code libraries and code examples for every encoding setting. 
                                        

                                            Unlimited scalability
                                        

                                            Up to 10x faster than other cloud transcoding solutions
                                        


Purpose


                                    Brightcove Zencoder is a powerful cloud transcoding platform that reduces operational cost and complexity, eliminates bandwidth bottlenecks, and provides viewers with a high quality user experience on their device of choice.
                                







Pricing


                                One Time Fee (Project, Sponsorship or Outright Purchase)
                            




