Headquartered in Boston, MA, Brightcove Inc. provides cloud-based solutions for publishing and distributing professional digital media. The company also has operations in Tokyo, Japan.
Headquartered in Boston, MA, Brightcove Inc. provides cloud-based solutions for publishing and distributing professional digital media. The company also has operations in Tokyo, Japan.

At Brightcove, Inc., the Vice President of Technical Operations is responsible for overseeing all internal information technology initiatives, as… MoreHeadquartered in Boston, MA, Brightcove Inc. provides cloud-based solutions for publishing and distributing professional digital media. The company also has operations in Tokyo, Japan.

At Brightcove, Inc., the Vice President of Technical Operations is responsible for overseeing all internal information technology initiatives, as well as product development and support. He is assisted by the Vice President of Engineering, who oversees all product development operations.

The Systems Engineering team is responsible for building, operating, scaling, and troubleshooting all of Brightcove's SaaS infrastructure and applications. The internal staff oversees all day-to-day infrastructure operations, including telecommunications, storage area networking, information security, server and systems administration, desktop support, and data center operations.





